    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/4093c280096ec45b2d26996fc3c24db4.poster.avif?t=1726051499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/4093c280096ec45b2d26996fc3c24db4.webm?t=1726051499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/4093c280096ec45b2d26996fc3c24db4.mp4?t=1726051499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>城市里一片混乱：当地动物园里的所有动物都逃出来了！海豹、狗、兔子、浣熊，全部需要营救并送回家！在勇敢的杰西卡的带领下，救援队迅速出发帮助大家，恢复城市的和平与秩序。激动人心的挑战等待着你！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/c7d7d44459b681611d4bd31224d6822f.poster.avif?t=1726051499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/c7d7d44459b681611d4bd31224d6822f.webm?t=1726051499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/c7d7d44459b681611d4bd31224d6822f.mp4?t=1726051499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>畅玩各种地点和紧急情况！<br>人们始终需要救援人员！在酒店、超市、餐馆、电影制片厂、游轮和农场展开救援。你将驾驶消防车，清除垃圾、重建道路、翻新建筑，拯救动物并喂给它们美味的食物。<br>尝试成为消防员、海滩救生员和紧急救援人员！要完成任务，你必须快速行动、聪明思考，并进行团队合作！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/149e6f894eedb491107cdcbecff67416.poster.avif?t=1726051499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/149e6f894eedb491107cdcbecff67416.webm?t=1726051499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/149e6f894eedb491107cdcbecff67416.mp4?t=1726051499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在任务过程中，你需要收集和使用资源。制定自己的战略，尽可能高效地完成任务。运用大脑取胜！并且不要忘记时间限制！尝试及时解决难题！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/19a390e7da6626dee52f426bd1fada0b.poster.avif?t=1726051499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/19a390e7da6626dee52f426bd1fada0b.webm?t=1726051499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254000/extras/19a390e7da6626dee52f426bd1fada0b.mp4?t=1726051499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
